               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Savior of the World, መልክአ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም፡, Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡, incomplete</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="16r" facs="002">Fols 1r–16r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2883RepCh164">Malkǝʾa madḫāne
                                                  ʿālam</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="16r" to="20v" facs="017">Fols 16r–20v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2927RepCh208">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለጽንሰትከ፡ ወለልደትከ፡ ቡሩክ። በበአለ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ዘዮም፡ ወመቀለ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ክርስ፡ አምላክ።
                  </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="21v" to="32r" facs="023">Fols 21v–32r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
